Product Description

Toshiba Full HD Smart TV is a new generation of television featuring the Fire TV experience built-in and including a Voice Remote with Alexa. Toshiba delivers a superior TV experience that gets smarter everyday and access to all the movies and TV shows you love. The Voice Remote with Alexa lets you do everything you'd expect from a remoteplus, easily launch apps, search for titles, play music, switch inputs, control smart home devices, and more, using your voice.

Smart but simple in every way. Just plug it in, connect to Wi-Fi, and enjoy.

Incredible value

Enjoy 1080p Full HD picture quality for lifelike detail, rich contrast, and brilliant colours . Toshiba is built for speed and performance. Its powered by a-quad-core CPU/Multi-core GPU for instant search results and fast and fluid responsiveness. Connect easily with dual-band Wi-Fi, three HDMI inputs and multiple input/output options. You can even customize the name of each input and adjust picture settings for each connected device. Plus, your TV keeps getting smarter with new Alexa skills and automatic over-the-air software updates, so you always have the latest.

Live TV + tens of thousands movies and TV episodes

Fire TV Edition brings together live over-the-air TV and all your streaming channels on the home screen. Connect any HD antenna and use Alexa to instantly search for and watch live over-the-air TV, or choose from a vast catalogue of streaming movies and TV shows from Netflix, Prime Video, CraveTV, and CTV and more. You can also connect your cable/satellite box or gaming console through one of the TV's three HDMI ports.

Control your TV

Use the included Voice Remote with Alexa to easily control TV functions like power, volume, navigation, playback and input switchingplus, easily launch into Netflix, Prime Video, CraveTV and CTV with quick access buttons.

Find new favourites

Want to watch something new? Press the microphone button and say, Find dramas, and Alexa will show you search results from a universal catalogue of integrated apps and channels.

Control your smart home

Enhance your entertainment experience by easily controlling your smart home devices with Alexa. Simply use your voice to do things like adjust the lights, set the temperature and lock the door and ease right into movie night.

Get more out of Alexa

Go beyond streaming with access to thousands of Alexa skills. Want to check the score? Play a game? Alexa can do that too!

How does Amazon calculate star ratings?
Amazon calculates a products star ratings using a machine learned model instead of a raw data average. The machine learned model takes into account factors including: the age of a review, helpfulness votes by customers and whether the reviews are from verified purchases.

1.0 out of 5 stars READ BEFORE YOU BUY
Reviewed in Canada on January 3, 2019
Size: 55 inchesStyle Name: 4K UHDVerified Purchase
This TV is not worth the money. The frame rate issues are evident across all content. I bought this TV at best buy during boxing day sales. Was completely disappointed with the product and brought it back. I sprung the $200 more for an LG and have none of the issues the Toshiba Fire was displaying in terms of frame rate, Studder ect.

Want to hook up an external hard drive with your downloaded content? Forget it. The USB drive will display JPEG's or act as an external storage for apps only. So for those that would like to enjoy their 4k downloads, forget it.

The only pros of the Toshiba Fire TV are it's voice controls and a few bells and whistles in the O.S.

Summary:
PROS:
-Client friendly OS
-Voice Control
-Comes with free Alexa

CONS
-Terribly buggy streaming across all content
-Studder, Frame Rate, Frame Clipping makes viewing 4k streaming content unpleasant.
-USB functionality is embarrassing
-Extremely poor view from the side effect

2 out of 10 at Best
